_sText: This map is meant to be a live action arcade shooter. It is single player, and has three games which percentage scoring. This is a work in progress, the games don't have levels yet, just single rounds, they do add in points though. This map is NOT meant to be put on a server though it does have nine spawn points, having more than one person can screw scoring up. Right now the only weapon spawn is in the green game. If you want weapons use "sv_cheats 1" and "give weapon_ak47" ect. If the screen shots do not make sense, download the map and play it.
